## Non-Negotiable Rules

- Polars only ‚Äî never pandas
- Pydantic v2 models everywhere ‚Äî no raw dicts
- MCP-first tool design ‚Äî every capability is a discoverable MCP tool
- LangGraph supervisor+subgraph orchestration only
- LiteLLM routing (caching mandatory)
- NautilusTrader for all backtest/optimize
- Score ‚â•8 Security, ‚â•8 Quality, ‚â•7 Optimization, ‚â•9 Accuracy before PR
- Never touch live-trading paths without explicit human approval

- **Every code change must trace to a GitHub Issue on Project #1.** Use a `task/<N>-<slug>` branch (via `make task ISSUE=N`) or include `Fixes #<N>` in the PR body. Enforced by `.github/workflows/pr-linkage.yml`.

